	"This function is to create a new tab with Startify window and NERDTree
	"window.
	function Start_NewTabAndNERDTree()
			execute ":tabnew"		
			execute ":Startify"		
			execute ":NERDTree"
			execute ":set nu"
			execute	":set cul"
			execute ":set nu"
		endfunction
"End here
